As a senator of ASUC and a part of one of these organizations this is highly offensive. ASUC at UC Berkeley make it their goal to give students a place to feel comfortable as well as better the community. Comparing specific parties to characters from a movie about bullying is absurd and beyond inaccurate. Making the claim that ASUC are cliques is demeaning the values they are founded on. This clearly is a stab at a community on campus that does nothing but support the rest of the student body.
